<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="description" content="Achme Enterprise Quotation Details Viewer." />
  <!-- Open Graph Metadata -->
  <meta property="og:title" content="Achme Quotation Viewer" />
  <meta property="og:description" content="View quotation and invoices generated by Achme Enterprise System." />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:url" content="https://achme.com" />
  <title>Quotation</title>

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #1a1f2e;
      --muted: #64748b;
      --line: #cbd5e1;
      --line-soft: #e2e8f0;
      --brand: #1e3a8a;
      --brand-deep: #1e293b;
      --paper: #ffffff;
      --page-bg: #f1f5f9;
      --shadow-sm: 0 2px 8px rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.08);
      --shadow-md: 0 8px 24px rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.10);
      --shadow-lg: 0 16px 48px rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.14);
      --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.96);
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html {
      -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
      print-color-adjust: exact;
    }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: var(--page-bg);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      padding: clamp(10px, 3vw, 30px);
    }

    .quotation-wrapper {
      position: relative;
      width: min(100%, 210mm);
      min-height: 297mm;
      margin: 0 auto;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: var(--paper);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
      padding: clamp(14px, 3vw, 9mm);
    }

    .quotation-wrapper::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 6px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #1f0779e0, #340285, #1b03a1);
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .watermark {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      max-width: 55%;
      max-height: 55%;
      width: auto;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      opacity: 0.07;
      pointer-events: none;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 12px rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.25));
      mix-blend-mode: multiply;
      z-index: 9998;
      object-fit: contain;
    }

    .content {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .header {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(210px, 1fr) auto;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: start;
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      border-bottom: 3px solid var(--brand);
    }

    .brand img {
      display: block;
      width: min(100%, 330px);
      height: auto;
    }

    .quotation-title {
      display: grid;
      justify-items: end;
      gap: 10px;
      text-align: right;
    }

    .quotation-title h2 {
      color: var(--brand);
      font-size: clamp(10px, 2.4vw, 22px);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 0.98;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .doc-box {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px 14px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      max-width: 100%;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      background: #f8fafc;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .doc-box span {
      color: var(--ink);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .top-boxes {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 12px;
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .info-box,
    .terms-box,
    .summary-box,
    .notes-box,
    .bank-box,
    .branch-box,
    .footer {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    .info-box {
      min-height: 166px;
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .box-title,
    .section-heading {
      color: var(--brand);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0;
    }

    .box-title {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .info-box h3 {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .gst {
      margin-bottom: 9px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .compact,
    .contact-line,
    .terms-box li,
    .notes-box,
    .bank-grid,
    .branch-box,
    .footer {
      font-size: 11.5px;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    .contact-line {
      display: flex;
      gap: 7px;
      align-items: baseline;
      margin-top: 7px;
      word-break: break-word;
    }

    .contact-line .label {
      min-width: 40px;
      color: var(--brand-deep);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .table-wrap {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 14px;
      overflow-x: auto;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: var(--paper);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    th {
      padding: 10px 8px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--brand);
      color: var(--brand-deep);
      font-size: 10.5px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-align: left;
      white-space: nowrap;
      background: #f8fafc;
    }

    td {
      padding: 10px 8px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line-soft);
      font-size: 11px;
      vertical-align: top;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    tbody tr:last-child td,
    .summary-table tr:last-child td {
      border-bottom: 0;
    }

    .summary-table {
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    }

    .summary-table td {
      padding: 9px 6px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .grand-total td {
      color: var(--brand);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 700;
      background: #f0f4ff;
    }

    td:last-child,
    th:last-child {
      text-align: right;
    }

    .mid-section {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .grid-2x2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .terms-box,
    .summary-box,
    .notes-box,
    .bank-box,
    .branch-box {
      padding: 12px;
    }

    .section-heading {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .terms-box ul {
      padding-left: 16px;
    }

    .bank-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 88px minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 7px 10px;
    }

    .bank-grid div:nth-child(odd) {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .branch-box {
      margin-top: 12px;
    }

    .footer {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px 20px;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
    }

    .footer span {
      color: var(--brand);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    @media (max-width: 760px) {
      body {
        padding: 0;
        background: var(--paper);
      }

      .quotation-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        min-height: auto;
        border: 0;
        box-shadow: none;
        padding: 14px;
      }

      .header,
      .top-boxes {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .grid-2x2 {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .brand img {
        width: min(100%, 280px);
      }

      .quotation-title {
        justify-items: start;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .doc-box {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }

      .info-box {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .table-wrap {
        overflow: visible;
        border: 0;
        border-radius: 0;
      }

      .table-wrap table,
      .table-wrap thead,
      .table-wrap tbody,
      .table-wrap tr,
      .table-wrap th,
      .table-wrap td {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .table-wrap thead {
        position: absolute;
        width: 1px;
        height: 1px;
        overflow: hidden;
        clip: rect(0 0 0 0);
      }

      .table-wrap tr {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        border: 1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: var(--paper);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .table-wrap td {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 112px minmax(0, 1fr);
        gap: 12px;
        padding: 9px 10px;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .table-wrap td::before {
        content: attr(data-label);
        color: var(--brand);
        font-size: 10px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }

      .table-wrap td:last-child {
        text-align: left;
      }

      .footer {
        justify-content: flex-start;
      }
    }

    @media print {
      @page {
        size: A4;
        margin: 0;
      }

      body {
        min-height: auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .quotation-wrapper {
        width: 210mm;
        min-height: 297mm;
        border: 0;
        box-shadow: none;
        padding: 8mm;
      }

      .watermark {
        max-width: 130mm;
        width: auto;
        height: auto;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        opacity: 0.12;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <main class="quotation-wrapper">
        <img class="watermark" src="./achme2logo high.jpg.jpeg" alt="Achme Communication watermark">


    <div class="content">
      <header class="header">
        <div class="brand">
          <img src="./achme logo high.jpg.jpeg" alt="Achme Communication logo">
        </div>

        <div class="quotation-title">
          <h2>QUOTATION</h2>

          <div class="doc-box">
            <div><span>Doc No:</span> QT-2026-045</div>
            <div><span>Date:</span> 10 Apr 2026</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

      <section class="top-boxes" aria-label="Quotation parties">
        <div class="info-box">
          <div class="box-title">FROM</div>

          <h3>Achme Communication</h3>
          <div class="gst">GSTIN: 33AABCA1234D1Z5</div>

          <div class="compact">
            436H Avinashi Road Opp to SMS Hotel,<br>
            Peelamedu
          </div>

          <div class="contact-line">
            <span class="label">Ph:</span>
            <span>0422-2569966, 4376555</span>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-line">
            <span class="label">Email:</span>
            <span>info@achmecommunication.com</span>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-line">
            <span class="label">Web:</span>
            <span>www.achmecommunication.com</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="info-box">
          <div class="box-title">BILLED TO</div>

          <h3>Madhratechnologies</h3>

          <div class="compact">madhura</div>

          <div class="contact-line">
            <span class="label">Ph:</span>
            <span>1234567890</span>
          </div>

          <div class="contact-line">
            <span class="label">Email:</span>
            <span>divyamadhuratech@gmail.com</span>
          </div>

          <div class="compact" style="margin-top: 10px;">
            no.6, new street, opposite to bank,<br>
            rspuram, coimbatore, tamilnadu,123456,India
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="table-wrap">
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>S.NO</th>
              <th>DESCRIPTION</th>
              <th>BRAND / MODEL</th>
              <th>QTY</th>
              <th>UOM</th>
              <th>PRICE</th>
              <th>TOTAL</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>

          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td data-label="S.NO">1</td>
              <td data-label="DESCRIPTION"><strong>mouse</strong></td>
              <td data-label="BRAND / MODEL">boAt</td>
              <td data-label="QTY">1</td>
              <td data-label="UOM">Units</td>
              <td data-label="PRICE">Rs. 500.00</td>
              <td data-label="TOTAL"><strong>Rs. 525.00</strong></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td data-label="S.NO">2</td>
              <td data-label="DESCRIPTION"><strong>keyboard</strong></td>
              <td data-label="BRAND / MODEL">Mivi</td>
              <td data-label="QTY">1</td>
              <td data-label="UOM">Sets</td>
              <td data-label="PRICE">Rs. 1,000.00</td>
              <td data-label="TOTAL"><strong>Rs. 1,050.00</strong></td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td data-label="S.NO">3</td>
              <td data-label="DESCRIPTION"><strong>HDMI cable</strong></td>
              <td data-label="BRAND / MODEL">Apple</td>
              <td data-label="QTY">1</td>
              <td data-label="UOM">Meters</td>
              <td data-label="PRICE">Rs. 199.00</td>
              <td data-label="TOTAL"><strong>Rs. 208.95</strong></td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <section class="mid-section" aria-label="Quotation details">
        <div class="grid-2x2">
          <div class="terms-box">
            <div class="section-heading">TERMS & CONDITIONS</div>

            <ul>
              <li>General Terms & Conditions apply.</li>
              <li>Prices quoted are exclusive of Sales and Service Tax.</li>
              <li>Project Period: 30-60 days from Purchase Order date.</li>
              <li>Quote valid for 15 days from quotation date.</li>
              <li>Price may vary based on USD rates.</li>
              <li>Payment Terms: 30 Days.</li>
              <li>Warranty: Testing Warranty.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="summary-box">
            <table class="summary-table">
              <tr>
                <td>Subtotal</td>
                <td>Rs. 1,699.00</td>
              </tr>

              <!-- <tr>
                <td>CGST (2.5%)</td>
                <td>Rs. 42.48</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td>SGST (2.5%)</td>
                <td>Rs. 42.48</td>
              </tr> -->

              <tr class="grand-total">
                <td>GRAND TOTAL</td>
                <!-- <td>Rs. 1,783.95</td> -->
                 <td>Rs. 1,699.00</td>
              </tr>
            </table>
          </div>

          <div class="notes-box">
            <div class="section-heading">IMPORTANT NOTES</div>

            <strong>Materials:</strong>
            BOQ based on discussion. Extra materials required at execution charged extra.
            CABLE & ACCESSORIES AS PER ACTUALS.
            <br><br>

            <strong>Delay:</strong>
            Delays due to external dependencies at site - Achme Communication will not be responsible.
            <br><br>

            <strong>NOTE:</strong>
            Civil, Electrical & Interior Works not included.
          </div>

          <div class="bank-box">
            <div class="section-heading">BANK DETAILS</div>

            <div class="bank-grid">
              <div>Company</div>
              <div><strong>Achme Communication</strong></div>

              <div>Bank</div>
              <div><strong>KOTAK MAHINDRA BANK</strong></div>

              <div>Account</div>
              <div><strong>12345667</strong></div>

              <div>IFSC</div>
              <div><strong>34DJFHJDH</strong></div>

              <div>Branch</div>
              <div><strong>Test, Coimbatore</strong></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="branch-box">
        <div class="section-heading">OUR BRANCHES</div>

        <strong>Bangalore:</strong>
        14th Main Road, GK Layout, Electronic City Post, Bangalore - 560100 |
        GSTIN: 2635GHHJG

        <br>

        <strong>Chennai:</strong>
        5th Floor, 5CD PM Towers, Dreams Road, Thousand Lights, Chennai - 600006 |
        GSTIN: 423523GSDH
      </div>

      <footer class="footer">
        <div><span>Executive:</span> kumar</div>
        <div><span>PH:</span> 12345678</div>
        <div><span>Email:</span> kumar@gmail.com</div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
